fields.descriptive_line: Scrabble, J W Spear & Sons Ltd, English, 1970s
fields.physical_description:
rectangular card box printed in colours to show the title in white and red on a green ground, together with the maker's details and an illustration of a scrabble board; interior printed with the rules of play (black on white); base of white card covered with white paper; insert of grey card, with the outer surfaces covered with white paper - it has four shallow sides with the corners reinforced with brown paper
contains playing surface, drawstring bag, tile racks and quantity of letter tiles
2-5  letter tile racks, grey plastic with angled surfaces and shaped ends
*square letter tiles, cream plastic with rounded corners and a circular hollow at the back; moulded and marked in black with a letter of the alphabet and its individual score
6-14  letter A 
15,16  letter B
17,18  letter C
19-22  letter D
23-34  letter E
35,36  letter F
37-39  letter G
40,41  letter H
42-50  letter I
51       letter J
52       letter K
53-56  letter L
57,58  letter M
59-64  letter N
65-72  letter O
73,74  letter P
75       letter Q
76-81  letter R
82-85  letter S
86-90  letter T
91-94  letter U
95,96  letter V
97,98  letter W
99       letter X
100,101  letter Y
102,103  blank tile
[games board] folding board for use with the game Scrabble
exterior covered with textured drk green paper with a cnetral hinge covered in black cotton
interior covered with grid layout, printed in white on a stone coloured ground, with black lettering and the special squares indicated in red, pink, pale blue and turquoise
[Bag] drawstring bag from which letter tile may be drawn during play
unlined polyester cotton blend, printed with a sprigged design of stylized flowers and foliage in pink, mauve and green on a white ground
white cotton tape drawstring threaded through a casing at the top edge of bag
fields.dimensions: length: 35.5 cm playing surface, width: 35.5 cm open, width: 19.8 cm bag, length: 22 cm bag, length: 36.5 cm box, width: 18.8 cm box, depth: 3.1 cm box, length: 17.3 cm tile rack, width: 2.3 cm tile rack, depth: 1.9 cm tile rack, length: 2 cm tile, width: 1.8 cm tile, depth: 0.6 cm tile
